[h4 id=AboutTheRun 
	" About the run
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/Angerfist 
		"Angerfist
	]a
	" started doing a MM8 TAS, but abandoned it later. It was then that I took the task of doing this hard-to-optimize but rewarding TAS.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Started Jan. 12, 2010. Ended Mar. 29, 2010.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"As a general rule of thumb, your TASes will always take much longer to do than you expected. Did I want to complete this TAS over 2.5 months? Of course not. (Did I want to complete this TAS? Yes!)
	$LF
