[h4 id=Wily1Stage 
	" Wily 1 stage
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Another JUMP JUMP SLIDE SLIDE. Capcom really wants you to die. Of course, this simply gives the opportunity for a TASer to twist the level some more. One not-well-known secret is that you can float Mega Man by using Thunder Claw, Flame Sword, or (best) Astro Crush.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"No, Rush Bike is not faster in the part after. Besides, would you rather see exciting Thunder Claw/slide/jump/destroy or boring Rush Bike?
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The boss kills my mind. D: D:
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[img class=embed mw-100 src=http://i19.photobucket.com/albums/b185/jhchan8/mm8/snap_061.png 
	]img
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Anyway, first of all, you can hit it before it even does anything. Just try and use Mega Ball right away. Second, you have to kill all the parts as fast as possible. No, Astro Crush does not work. I have to use a combination of Ice Wave, Flash Bomb, and Mega Ball. Basically, I manipulate the main part in one of the inside slots. Then I do this:
	$LF
]div
[table 
	[tbody 
		[tr 
			[th 
				"Slot1
			]th
			[th 
				"Slot2
			]th
			[th 
				"Slot3
			]th
			[th 
				"Slot4
			]th
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"Energy box
			]td
			[td 
				"Attack part
			]td
			[td 
				"Main part
			]td
			[td 
				"Attack part
			]td
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"Flash Bomb here 2->
			]td
			[td 
				"<-Flash Bomb here 2
			]td
			[td 
				"Mega Ball it 3
			]td
			[td 
				"Ice Wave it 1
			]td
		]tr
	]tbody
]table
[div class=p 
	"There. A table to describe something which could have easily been described in 200 words.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"No matter how fast you do it, there is a minimum delay until the click sound (which starts the next cycle), so I don't frame whore. There is a delay between the click sound and when it comes down, which is manipulated to be as small as possible.
	$LF
]div
