[div class=p 
	"It's not that long though, trust me. And you get to do a little more.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Anyway, the boss is a huge ship. Yes, Capcom did their best to remind you it's an autoscroller. The ship dies to Astro Crush. I manipulated it so it did the attacks it does here, and that it spits out as few spiked balls as possible (6). Mind you, it's not possible to defeat it in one cycle. Even if it does its charge attack first. Also, doing charge attack first resets its path going upward, whereas I want it to be as low as possible when it dies.
	$LF
]div
