[div class=p 
	"The second form is long. You can only hit him once per cycle. I empty my stock because I have nothing else to do really. Wily does one of two attacks when he appears on the bottom. You'll see this often because he is unhittable when on the top, unless I use Tornado Hold. On the top, he has a couple other attacks. Last hit, I manipulate so he appears on the bottom right, where he ends up when he dies.
	$LF
